{
  "style": "IEEE",
  "texts": [
    "It utilizes soft-prompt tuning to learn natural language prompts for specific tasks.",
    "Several works [59], [101], [102], [110], [111] have used this approach for medical text classification.",
    "For instance, PBP [101] used SciBERT [110] as the backbone model and learned natural language prompts that can classify medical texts.",
    "NapSS [102] used GPT-2 [59] as the backbone model and learned natural language prompts that can generate personalized recommendations for clinical scenarios.",
    "MedRoBERTa.nl [111] used soft-prompt tuning to learn natural language prompts that can classify medical texts into different categories."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
